---
title: Bangladeshi-Style Shrimp & Green Beans with Basmati Rice & Cilantro
description: In celebration of Asian Heritage Month, we offer a taste of classic Bangladeshi home cooking. Fragrant basmati rice is served alongside juicy, quick-cooking shrimp and crisp-tender green beans sautéed with onion, cumin, curry, and garam masala. It’s finished with butter and garlic for a rich, flavorful sauce, and sprinkled with cilantro for a dash of fresh herbaceousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/661d659ab4db7806c6d9dee8-1b6d37cb.jpeg
